headline: 3 Stocks That Could Skyrocket Before the End of 2024
summary: The Federal Reserve is set to meet in the middle of December, and it has signaled a desire to cut interest rates further at that time.  When it cut rates in September, the stock market had an extremely positive reaction, and another cut could activate more market enthusiasm.  Mortgage rates began to go down when interest rates were cut, but they're going back up.

headline: FIFA welcomes The Home Depot as Official Home Improvement Retail Supporter for FIFA World Cup 26™ in North America
summary: FIFA and The Home Depot are teaming up to bring the excitement of the FIFA World Cup 26™ to life across North America. As the world's largest home improvement retailer, with stores throughout Canada, Mexico and the USA where the tournament is to take place, The Home Depot will be the Official Home Improvement Retail Supporter in the region.
